        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【教学】AI 影片字幕制造机 WhisperDesktop    广东话、外语片制 CC 字幕 + Windows 免费用</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/whisper-gui-windows-free-to-use/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=whisper-gui-windows-free-to-use</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/whisper-gui-windows-free-to-use/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 10:00:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Whisper]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[WhisperDesktop]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[剪片]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[字幕]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286719</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>随著语音辨识技术迅速进步，OpenAI 推出的「Whisper」已经成为众多使用者心中的语音辨识首选。Whisper 以其强大的准确性和开源特性，成为免费且高效的自动生成字幕工具。然而安装过程和操作方式仍然稍显困难。今日小编会和大家分享一个全新的方法——WhisperDesktop。这个方法工具简化原本繁琐的操作流程，用户无需再使用指令，也能轻松进行语音辨识，自动生成字幕、文字稿等。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200055-694x382.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="382" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200055-694x382.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200055.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲原本没有字幕的影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287371" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937.jpg 909w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲使用今日介绍的 WhisperDesktop 后</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200012-425x580.png" alt="" width="425" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200012-425x580.png 425w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116200012.png 594w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 425px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即可一键影片语音转文字，还可以帮你加上 Timecode</p><h2>Step 1 下载 WhisperDesktop</h2><p>要使用 WhisperDesktop GUI，首先需要在 GitHub 下载桌面程式，截稿前最新版本为 1.12。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287288" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper_1-689x580.png" alt="" width="689" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper_1-689x580.png 689w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper_1.png 1069w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 689px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲请下载标明「Lastest」最新版本之程式</p><p>下载「WhisperDesktop.zip」压缩档（下图绿框示）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287291" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper2-694x396.png" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper2-694x396.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper2.png 1208w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下载「WhisperDesktop.zip」</p><p>下载完毕后你需要解压缩，解压缩后你会看见文件夹内一共有 3 个档案，其中有向日葵图案的就是 WhisperDesktop 程式，不要移动其余档案，点击即可开始设定，不过目前为止仍然未需要开启「WhisperDesktop.exe」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287295" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper3-1-694x462.png" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper3-1-694x462.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper3-1.png 1169w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以后只需点击「向日葵」图案即可使用</p><h2>Step 2 下载语言模组</h2><p>下载完 WhisperDesktop 后，并不代表我们可以立即使用这个程式语音转文字。接下来我们需要到 Hugging Face 下载相关语言模型。（<a href="https://huggingface.co/ggerganov/whisper.cpp/tree/main">下载连结</a>）。甫打开模型库会发觉琳瑯满目，但如果你和小编一样是业余用途，就只需要选择「Medium」模型。「Medium」模型兼顾准确性、生成速度及硬件需求，对一般用家来讲算是够用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287299" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116165930-605x580.jpg" alt="" width="605" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116165930-605x580.jpg 605w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116165930.jpg 938w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 605px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲打开模型库时的画面</p><p>同时按下 Ctrl+F，输入 medium 后就可以马上找到全部 medium 模型。今次小编会示范使用 ggml-medium.bin，点击下图红色箭嘴指住的下载键即可开始下载「ggml-medium.bin」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287301" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper5-694x279.png" alt="" width="694" height="279" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper5-694x279.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper5.png 1269w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击红色箭嘴指住的下载键下载 ggml-medium.bin（绿框示）</p><p>下载完成后，将「ggml-medium.bin」档案移动至刚才有向日葵图案「WhisperDesktop.exe」的文件夹。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116172542-694x459.png" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116172542-694x459.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116172542.png 1188w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲将 bin 档移至 WhisperDesktop 的文件夹</p><h2>Step 3 开始设定 WhisperDesktop</h2><p>将「ggml-medium.bin」移动至 WhisperDesktop 文件夹后，你就可以开始设定 WhisperDesktop。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287311" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper6-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper6-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/whisper6.png 1185w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「向日葵」图案使用</p><p>接下来你需要点击「…」（红箭嘴示）开启你的 ggml。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173350-694x466.png" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173350-694x466.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173350.png 860w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「…」</p><p>载入刚才的 ggml-medium 模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173542-694x385.png" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173542-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116173542.png 1252w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲双击选择刚才的模型</p><p>现时回到 WhisperDesktop，检查 Model Path 是否刚才选择的 ggml 模型，如正确就不要调整任何设定，保留其他设定为预设值后点击「ok」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116180542-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116180542-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116180542.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲检查 Model Path 是否刚才选择的 ggml 模型，如正确就点击 ok</p><h2>Step 4 开始使用</h2><p>稍等一阵就可载入完模型，之后你会看见下图画面，点击「Language」选项，选择「Chinese」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116181354-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116181354-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116181354.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择「Chinese」</p><p>之后你可以在「Output Format」选择输出甚么格式的文字稿：</p><ul><li>如果你要纯文字逐字稿，可选择「Text file」；</li><li>如果你想要生成 YouTube 的「CC 字幕」（有 Time Code），那么就需要选择「Subrip subtitles」输出 SRT 档案。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287355" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116185715-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116185715-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116185715.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择所需格式</p><p>之后点击「…」，选择你需要转为文字的影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287356" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190241-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190241-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190241.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「…」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287357" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190406-694x385.png" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190406-694x385.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190406.png 1249w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择所需影片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190629-694x472.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="472" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190629-694x472.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116190629.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择所需影片</p><p>选择完影片后，点击「Transcribe」开始语音转文字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「Transcribe」开始语音转文字</p><h2>实测：转换 15 分 25 秒 mp4 影片需时</h2><p>以下小编会使用一条 15 分 25 秒的 MP4 测试 WhisperDesktop 语音转换文字的速度。小编使用的电脑为 ASUS Zenbook Flip 14，采用内置显示卡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191813-422x580.png" alt="" width="422" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191813-422x580.png 422w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191813.png 528w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 422px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小编测试影片长度为 15:25</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116191739.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「Transcribe」开始语音转文字</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287371" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193937.jpg 909w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可在进度条检查转换进度</p><p>完成后会弹出一个提示视窗，告诉你耗时多久。WhisperDesktop 主要使用 GPU 转录为纯文字，而由于小编的电脑没有独立显示卡，因此耗时约 14 分钟方完成。如果你的电脑显示卡比较厉害，那么可以用更短时间完成转录工作。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195343-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195343-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195343.jpg 996w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲完成后会弹出视窗提示你</p><p>现在开启影片所在文件夹，你会看见 .srt 档案，这个就是你的 CC 字幕档。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287369" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193547-694x394.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="394" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193547-694x394.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193547.jpg 1172w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲生成的 .srt 字幕档</p><p>普通点击无法开启 .srt 档案，你需要选择以「记事本」开启。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287370" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193806-694x515.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="515" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193806-694x515.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116193806.jpg 881w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲选择以「记事本」开启 .srt 字幕档</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287373" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195420-277x580.png" alt="" width="277" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195420-277x580.png 277w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250116195420.png 429w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 277px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲现在你就可以看见你的 CC 字幕文字稿了</p><h2>总结：无须使用大量指令，图形介面直观完成工作</h2><p>对于那些不熟悉终端机指令的用户来说，WhisperDesktop 显然是一个更具亲和力的选择。WhisperDesktop 简化了安装和操作过程，并将繁琐的步骤图像化，让每个人都能轻松上手。</p><p>总结来说，Whisper GUI 是一款实用的工具，适合各类需求的用户。如果你曾因为难度较高的安装或操作流程而放弃使用 Whisper，那么这款 GUI 介面将无疑大幅简化你的使用体验，让语音辨识过程更加顺畅，无需过高电脑技术。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/whisper-gui-windows-free-to-use/ai/">【教学】AI 影片字幕制造机 WhisperDesktop    广东话、外语片制 CC 字幕 + Windows 免费用</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
